      "--------------------\n",
      "## Information ##\n",
      "<class 'pandas.DataFrame'>\n",
      "RangeIndex: 1000 entries, 0 to 999\n",
      "Data columns (total 21 columns):\n",
      " #   Column                   Non-Null Count  Dtype\n",
      "---  ------                   --------------  -----\n",
      " 0   status                   1000 non-null   str  \n",
      " 1   duration                 1000 non-null   int64\n",
